response.original_title: Hitting The Highspots - The UK Edition
response.overview: ob Naylor sits down with some of the top British Indy wrestling talent today in Marty Scurll, Will Ospreay and Mark Andrews. This interview was conducted just a few hours removed from the emotional conclusion to the 2015 Battle of Los Angeles Stage Three Event.  All three men are still on such a high from the event, they talk in great detail about how important BOLA was for them. Each has their own story on how they got there and Rob Naylor was able to bring those stories into the light. So, sit back and enjoy Rob Naylor is Hitting the Highspots with this British trio.
response.title: Hitting The Highspots - The UK Edition
